        {
            "title": "歐霸｜曼聯多古博完12碼主動要求取消 艾摩廉：做得好！ 網民一致激讚",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曼聯左閘多古。AFP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3b4f993bbd1548ab7e14d1ad084fb40e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031412172039029.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曼聯左閘多古。AFP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周四歐霸16強次回合，曼聯主場4:1大炒皇家蘇斯達，兩回合贏5:2晉級。其中一幕成賽後熱話，曼聯新兵多古末段本博得12碼，但他主動向球證澄清對方沒有犯規要求取消極刑，其後VAR亦推翻判決。此舉盡展體育精神，獲主帥魯賓艾摩廉大讚，網民亦一致大讚他此子有風度。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"球證本判12碼。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ea88f4b8fdcffcf0b3b9e511c62e6c0/2025-03/Gl9TrqNWIAENwFk.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        球證本判12碼。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多古要求取消12碼。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8ba140e4bc98b07260a8aaedb67b7bd/2025-03/Gl9TrxWWEAAsi99.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多古要求取消12碼。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯左閘多古博得12碼。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/044f12e212af37881265f94a14500e97/2025-03/2025-03-13T211149Z_2135409106_UP1EL3D1MVNE7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-MUN-RSO-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯左閘多古博得12碼。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯左閘多古博得12碼。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14ba3ca2d0ed5f40b300a55aece9c9bf/2025-03/AFP__20250313__372A6MA__v1__HighRes__FblEurC3ManUtdRealSociedad.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯左閘多古博得12碼。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯左閘多古。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/259edc7e441e63177800ceb6a334fc34/2025-03/AFP__20250207__36XD97D__v1__HighRes__FblEngFaCupManUtdLeicester.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯左閘多古。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯左閘多古。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d94dbbbc21b8f179904f84ba5520169b/2025-03/2025-02-07T204212Z_1520916429_UP1EL271LIAA9_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-LEI-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯左閘多古。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>多古主動要求取消12碼</h2>\n<p>事發於85分鐘，多古在一次進攻中博得12碼，雖然當時曼聯只領先2:1，總比數領先3:2，但多古依然非常誠實地主動向球證表示沒有被對手侵犯要求取消12碼，而VAR檢查後亦裁定並非12碼。不過曼聯最後都再連入2球，順利贏4:1。\n\n</p><h2>獲艾摩廉大讚</h2>\n<p>對於多古的君子行為，主帥艾摩廉先是大讚道：「這是好事，我為多古感到自豪。」不過，艾摩廉也笑言：「也要看情況。如果當時我們正落後，或者只是打和，我未必有一樣的回應了。但事實是多古今場表現很出色。」\n\n</p><h2>網民一致讚好</h2>\n<p>至於網民則一致讚揚這名丹麥國腳的高尚行為，有人指：「這種行為在現今足球真的很罕見，十分有體育精神。」另有人稱：「多古是誠實的孩子，做得好！」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058103/即時-體育-歐霸-曼聯多古博完12碼主動要求取消-艾摩廉-做得好-網民一致激讚",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 12:21:36",
